long_description: the rise and growth of the mobile phone retail industry in chennai has been analogous to that of priyadarshini cell universe. since its inception in 2004, it has made remarkable strides as a smartphone retailer catering to the popular demands of the clients. the story behind the founding of the brand is as inspiring as it is ambitious. according to the founder, this has endeared the customers to his organization. "once we offered 10 cellphones free on the purchase of one phone. there are no sham slogan contests or draw of lots. these offers remain unmatched and have created a lot of buzz around the band. with the emergence of smartphones, their accompanying gadgets, and accessories, priyadarshini cell universe too had to reinvent itself. "people are very aware these days. the mobile store is also focusing on servicing clients and enabling them to purchase their dream phone brands without parting with a fortune at one go. "there was a time when not everyone could afford a cellphone, but nowadays everyone owns one.
